column5: Does anyone know the dates of the two tourneys held on the Winnipeg River out of Pine Falls? I know theres one on the weekend of Canadas Thankgiving, but need to know the date of theother one.
Usually they are the first and third weekends of October. You can find a website that may give you teh information that you are looking for at http://virtualnorth.com/walleye/.
Look on this sites main page under INFORMATION and then go to TOURMNAMENTS
Look on this sites main page under INFORMATION and then go to TOURNAMENTS
